# restcontroller_requestparam

## What I Learned
- how to make traversal by using bfs
- Understanding of Queue from error I made
- If there's **null** value in queue, queue is **not empty**

## error code
    @PostMapping("/insert")
    public ResponseEntity<?> insert(BoardDTO board)
            throws IllegalStateException, IOException {
        log.info(board.toString());
        service.insert(board);

        return ResponseEntity.ok(HttpStatus.OK);
    }



## fixed code
    @PostMapping("/insert")
    public ResponseEntity<?> insert(**@RequestBody** BoardDTO board)
            throws IllegalStateException, IOException {
        log.info(board.toString());
        service.insert(board);

        return ResponseEntity.ok(HttpStatus.OK);
    }

    
